Package me.dessie.dessielib.storageapi.api

Class StorageAPI

java.lang.Object
me.dessie.dessielib.storageapi.api.StorageAPI
All Implemented Interfaces:
IStorageAPI
Direct Known Subclasses:
CoreStorageAPI, SpigotStorageAPI
public abstract class StorageAPI extends Object implements IStorageAPI
Abstraction class that generically defines and overrides the majority of the required methods for a StorageAPI implementation.

    • addStorageDecomposer

      public void addStorageDecomposer(StorageDecomposer<?> decomposer)
      Description copied from interface: IStorageAPI
      Adds a StorageDecomposer that can be accessed through all StorageContainer instances. These only need to be added once, and a class can only have 1 StorageDecomposer. Attempting to add a second StorageDecomposer for a class will overwrite the first one.
      Specified by:
      addStorageDecomposer in interface IStorageAPI
      Parameters:
      decomposer - The StorageDecomposer to add.
